arStrings.szText: Follow Neyrelle's journey in Nahantu through the {c_highlight}Vessel of Hatred{/c} expansion.
Lilith has been defeated, but there is still much to do. Level up to take on new challenges across the continent.
Seasonal Content is now unlocked! Follow the {icon:Quest_Season_Progress, 2.5}Season Quest marker to learn more.

You can also complete {c_highlight}Whispers of the Dead{/c}, participate in {c_highlight}Helltide{/c}, and challenge yourself in {c_highlight}The Pit{/c} to gain valuable items and crafting materials to progress your character.
Continue unlocking the Expanded Difficulty Progression to gain access to more powerful items.
